summary: Jump into the Spider-Verse for the Best Spider-Man Tale to Hit the Big Screen
title: Jump into the Spider-Verse for the Best Spider-Man Tale to Hit the Big Screen
body:
Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse is fresh and stylish fun, even if you’re exhausted by the endless rebooting of the Spider-Franchise.

Over the past two decades, there have been somewhere around 67 different Spider-Mans (Spider-Men?) swinging into theaters as part of their respective re-reboots of the franchise. It’s easy to feel exhausted at the idea of sitting through yet another Spidey origin story, disillusioned by all the awfulness to come before it. But not this time. Sony’s animated Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Versedouble…
